      <title>苹果 Beats 推出带心率监测功能的 Powerbeats Pro 2</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-11/apple-s-beats-launches-250-powerbeats-pro-2-with-heart-rate-monitoring</link>
